          {
            "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12688286/comment/13868098",
            "id": "13868098",
            "author": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=kkambatl",
              "name": "kkambatl",
              "key": "kkambatl",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Karthik Kambatla",
              "active": false,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "bq. Given that the RM already formats an empty store, why do we need this?\nThe usecase I have in mind is more for a non-empty store. When using the ZK-store, if we decide to tear down the cluster and start a new one using the same quorum, tearing down requires explicitly resetting the ACLs on the root-znode (changed during fencing) and then deleting the znode structure. \n\nbq. Having formatting in 2 places will require both to be kept in sync.\nWe can abstract it out to one method, which both places use. This method would require a force boolean to format non-empty stores? ",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=kkambatl",
              "name": "kkambatl",
              "key": "kkambatl",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Karthik Kambatla",
              "active": false,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "created": "2014-01-10T18:35:20.762+0000",
            "updated": "2014-01-10T18:35:20.762+0000"
          },
          {
